targets.rawSql:
SELECT "Party"."FirstName","Party"."LastName","Party"."Email","Status","AccessRequest"."RequestedOn","DigitalEvidence"."ParticipantId", "AccessRequest"."Modified" - "AccessRequest"."RequestedOn" as "Duration"
FROM "AccessRequest","Party","DigitalEvidence"
 WHERE "AccessRequest"."PartyId" = "Party"."Id" 
 AND "DigitalEvidence"."Id" = "AccessRequest"."Id" 
 AND "DigitalEvidence"."OrganizationName" = 'BC Prosecution Service'
 AND "AccessRequest"."RequestedOn" >= $__timeFrom() 
 order by "RequestedOn" DESC

panels.description: Amount of time in seconds to complete on-boarding

targets.rawSql:
SELECT "Party"."FirstName",
       ROUND(EXTRACT(epoch FROM ("AccessRequest"."Modified" - "AccessRequest"."RequestedOn"))) as DurationInSeconds
FROM "AccessRequest","Party","DigitalEvidence"
WHERE "AccessRequest"."PartyId" = "Party"."Id" 
AND "DigitalEvidence"."Id" = "AccessRequest"."Id" 
AND "DigitalEvidence"."OrganizationName" = 'BC Prosecution Service'
AND "AccessRequest"."RequestedOn" >= $__timeFrom() 
ORDER BY "RequestedOn" DESC

panels.title: Onboarding Duration (seconds)

targets.rawSql:
SELECT date_trunc('day', "RequestedOn") as day, count(*) as requests
FROM "AccessRequest"
GROUP BY day

panels.description: Number of case requests for a Submitting Agency

targets.rawSql:
select count(*), ol."Name",sar."RequestStatus", to_char( sar."RequestedOn", 'YYYY-MM') as month  from "SubmittingAgencyRequest" sar
left join "Party" p ON sar."PartyId"  = p."Id"
left join "PartyOrgainizationDetail" pod on pod."PartyId" = p."Id"
left join "OrganizationLookup" ol on ol."Code" = pod."OrganizationCode" 
where sar."RequestedOn" >= $__timeFrom() 
group by ol."Name",sar."RequestStatus",to_char( sar."RequestedOn", 'YYYY-MM')

panels.title: Case Requests By SA Per Month

targets.rawSql: SELECT COUNT(UPPER("Status")), UPPER("Status") FROM "AccessRequest" GROUP BY UPPER("Status")
